== Aswonvos ==
Yn 1986 apoyntys veu an peswar tyller avel ertachva an bys UNESCO. Henwys yns avel "Kastylli ha Fosow Tre Myghtern Edward yn Gwynedd".

UNESCO a brederas an tylleryow avel an  "ensamplow gwella a bennserneth kasorek an kansvledhen 13ves diwedhes ha 14ves a-varr yn Europa". <ref name="UNESCO" /> UNESCO ynwedh a leveris a-dro dhe boos aga hevrennow gans Edward I ha Jamys a Sen Jory, aga myns ha pennserneth kasorek avonsys, aga studh fest da ha dogvennow istorek. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://cadw.wales.gov.uk/docs/cadw/publications/WHS_part_2_EN.pdf|title=Part 2: Significance and Vision|publisher=Cadw|pages=44–45|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324104256/http://cadw.wales.gov.uk/docs/cadw/publications/WHS_part_2_EN.pdf|archive-date=24 March 2012|accessdate=15 November 2012|url-status=dead}}</ref> 

